import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux';
import { logout } from './your-redux-slice'; // Replace with your actual path

const Home = () => {
  const user = useSelector((state) => state.user);
  const dispatch = useDispatch();

  const handleLogout = () => {
    dispatch(logout());
  };

  return (
    <Box sx={{ mt: 10, bgcolor: '#f5f5f5', py: 8 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 4, bgcolor: 'white', borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)' }}>
              <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333' }}>
                Bienvenue au Tribunal de Commerce de Casablanca
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph sx={{ lineHeight: 1.6 }}>
                Application moderne et réactive pour la gestion du Tribunal de Commerce de Casablanca. Facilitant l'accès aux services et informations.
              </Typography>

              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                {user ? (
                  <Button variant="contained" color="primary" onClick={handleLogout} sx={{
                    bgcolor: '#d32f2f',
                    '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#c62828' },
                    color: 'white',
                    padding: '12px 24px',
                    borderRadius: '8px',
                    fontSize: '16px'
                  }}>
                    Se Déconnecter
                  </Button>
                ) : (
                  <Link to="/login" style={{ textDecoration: 'none' }}>
                    <Button variant="contained" color="primary" sx={{
                      bgcolor: '#007bff',
                      '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#0056b3' },
                      color: 'white',
                      padding: '12px 24px',
                      borderRadius: '8px',
                      fontSize: '16px'
                    }}>
                      Se Connecter
                    </Button>
                  </Link>
                )}
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 4, bgcolor: 'white', borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)' }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333' }}>
                Fonctionnalités
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des utilisateurs
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des réservations
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Gestion des départements
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} md={6}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 4, bgcolor: 'white', borderRadius: 2, boxShadow: '0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)' }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#333' }}>
                Avantages
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Facile à utiliser
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Conception réactive
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
                Sécurisé
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
